data.description: Welcome to Warren Road's hidden gem! This 3-bed, 2-bath charmer sits on a half-acre lot. Step inside to discover oak hardwood floors, a bright living room, and an inviting kitchen. The primary bedroom features a modern ensuite. Outside, a fenced yard with a patio and a 12'' x 20'' workshop awaits. With a perfect blend of original character and updates, this home is ideally located close to shopping, dining, parks, and schools. Don't miss this unique opportunity!
